*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
*.pyc

# Project Manager worker state (runtime audit trail, per-environment).
# Any project that hosts a PM worker via `claude-worker start --pm --cwd .`
# ends up with this directory. Contents are logs of chats and actions
# the PM observed — environment-specific, potentially sensitive, and
# not something that should travel in git.
.claude-worker-pm/
